    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It would be very disruptive to have `addWidget` return the same value as the parameter, it would break the chainable pattern expectation. In the chainable pattern the expected return value is the main object itself so you can continue doing more operations on the same object (like in jQuery).\n",
